Subject: CORRECTION - WINTER REGISTRATION OPENS AT NOON ON TUESDAY, JANUARY 7 - UPdate GradProSkills From: "GradProSkills" <gradproskills@concordia.ca> Date: 2014/1/6 17:39 To: wkkustc@gmail.com
Connect UPdate is the GradProSkills bi-weekly newsletter that highlights FREE skills training resources for current graduate students and postdoctoral fellows at Concordia. Add gradproskills@concordia.ca to your 'safe' email list.
NOTE REGISTRATION FOR WINTER 2014 WORKSHOPS OPENS AT NOON ON TUESDAY, JANUARY 7.
In this issue...
New Graduate Student Workshops, Essentials for TAs and Teaching, Meet Your Writing Deadlines, Research Conversations, Careers in and Beyond the Academy, Meet the Entrepreneur, Your Favourites & the GradProBlog launch
